
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/css/materialize.min.css">
    
    <title>Image Metadata Management System</title>
    <style>
        .btn-submit {
			background: rgba(57, 136, 255, 0.5);
			outline: none;
			width: 100px;
			padding-top: 0px;
			padding-bottom: 5px;
			padding-left: 5px;
			padding-right: 5px;
			margin-top: 20px;
			border-color: rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.2);
			border-radius: 5%;
			font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 18px;
			color: #242323;
		}

		.btn-submit:hover {
			background: rgba(57, 136, 255, 0.8);
			cursor:pointer;
		}
    </style>
</head>

<body style="text-align: center;">
    <br>
    <br>
    <form method="POST" action="/descfind">
		<label for="name">Type of the image you want in a single word</label>
		<input type="text" name="description" style="width: 100px;">

		<button class="btn-submit" type="submit">Search</button>
	</form>
	<p>Please note that image is searched based on "Image Description" property of image. So, The output sometimes might not have related image/no image at all for the requested query.</p>

    <div class="hi">
      <div class="form">
        <h4><b>Search</b></h4>
        <form method="post" action="/find">
            <label for="name">Key1</label>
            <input type="text" name="name1" style="width: 80px;">
            
            <label for="name">Key2</label>
            <input type="text" name="name2" style="width: 80px;">
            
            <label for="name">Value</label>
            <input type="text" name="prop" style="width: 80px;">
            
            <button class="btn-submit" type="submit">Search</button>
        </form>
      </div>



      <div class="container" style="max-width: 400px;">
          <h4><b>File Upload</b></h4>
          <br>
          <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
              <div class="file-field input-field">
                  <div style="background-color:red;" class="btn grey">
                      <span ><b>Select File</b></span>
                      <input name="myImage" type="file">

                      
                  </div>
                  <div class="file-path-wrapper">
                      <input class="file-path validate" type="text">
                  </div>
              </div>
              <br>
              <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Upload</button>
          </form>
          <br> <h6>Preview of previous upload:</h6>
          <img src="<%= typeof file != 'undefined' ? file : '' %>" class="responsive-img" style="max-height: 80px;">
      </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <h4 class="ex">Example Meta Data:</h4>
    <img src="exampleData.jpeg" alt="">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-hwg4gsxgFZhOsEEamdOYGBf13FyQuiTwlAQgxVSNgt4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/js/materialize.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
